<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-19 01:05 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2594 &Cx1f; tth-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-WHALE-SPI &LR;      05-19 1027
