 &HT;    Spotlight on. . . .
 &HT;    Staff reports
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News ServiceStanley Tucci (``The Impostors,''
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``William Shakespeare's A Midsummer Night's Dream'')
</P>
<P>
   ``Big Night'' (1996) _ As one of two brothers who own an Italian
restaurant that's being overshadowed by a flashy new trattoria.
</P>
<P>
   ``Mrs. Parker and the Vicious Circle'' (1994) _ As one of the
members of the witty, bantering Algonquin round table.
</P>
<P>
   ``Undercover Blues'' (1993) _ As a hapless petty crook who gets
in the way of spies Kathleen Turner and Dennis Quaid.
</P>
<P>
   ``Prelude to a Kiss'' (1992) _ As a workplace pal of Alec
Baldwin's in this romantic comedy.
</P>
<P>
   ``Billy Bathgate'' (1991) _ As gangster Lucky Luciano.
</P>
