<P>
   Rabin refused. Barak may accept. So goodbye, Arafat would
conclude, to another bit of Palestine. &QL; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; (350-WORD OPTIONAL TRIM BEGINS HERE AT 850) &LR;  &QC; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Certainly, a peace with Syria would allow Israel to withdraw
