<P>
   QUICK-REFUERBISH (New York) _ Carey Maloney and Hermes Mallea,
the designers of M (Group), were reeling their rolodexes and
flexing their shopping-arm muscles on behalf of Barry Gesser, a
single, 35-year-old hedge-fund manager who had purchased a house in
