<HEADER>
A3366 &Cx1f; tab-z
r l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HOME-IMPROVEMENT-BUDG     05-19 0332
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-HOME-IMPROVEMENT-BUDGET-ADV06-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
BUDGET: HOME IMPROVEMENT QUESTIONS AND ANSWERS
</HEADLINE>
  By BERNARD GLADSTONE 
