<HEADLINE>
STAR STRUCK? CHECK OUT YOUR WEEK 
 FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE 
 FROM THE FORT WORTH STAR-TELEGRAM
</HEADLINE>
  World rights. 
 By Students SARABETH BALON and NICK FOREMAN 
 Copyright 1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
 (Distributed by New York Times Special Features) 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Before finalizing your activities, take time to read the
following horoscope, which is a fun way to plan your week.
</P>
<P>
   GEMINI (May 21 - June 20): This week, you will be presented with
many options as far as summer activities are concerned. You had
better choose wisely, or your summer may be a complete and total
flop. Think about the people concerned and the fun you will have.
</P>
<P>
   CANCER (June 21 - July 22): Oftentimes you are too soft-hearted
when it comes to sticking with decisions. This week, when you make
a difficult decision about something, stick to it. Otherwise,
people will come to expect that you will not be firm in any choice
you make; they may play on your weaknesses.
</P>
<P>
   LEO (July 23 - Aug. 22): All you ever do is run around looking
for someone to be interested in you as a boy/girlfriend. If you
would just stop, then the perfect person would probably come
straight into your arms. Make it a point not to concentrate on the
lack of a significant other in your life this week.
</P>
<P>
   VIRGO (Aug. 23 - Sept. 22): Things consistently go well for you.
Be sure you are aware of this when people come to you for advice.
They are judging from the veneer, and it may help to show them a
new perspective. Give them a look at the behind-the-scenes action,
and it may ease their pain.
</P>
<P>
   LIBRA (Sept. 23 - Oct. 22): Start planning your
end-of-the-school-year party when you can clearly see the end of
the tunnel. You do not want to get so caught up in what you are
going to do after school that you fail to perform during school,
when it matters the most. As you start to turn in all of your
projects, put some extra oomph in them and try to get the ``A.''
</P>
<P>
   SCORPIO (Oct. 23 - Nov. 21): This week will have every kind of
test and challenge in it. By Thursday, it will be apparent to your
friends and family that you are not in a rational state of mind.
However, if you can make it through Thursday, you might be able to
coast into next week. Make time to have fun this weekend, but make
even more time to catch up on sleep.
</P>
<P>
   SAGITTARIUS (Nov. 22 - Dec. 21): You might find yourself being
abnormally free this week. Both your time and your privileges will
seem to open up, and you might not know how to react. However, if
you spend more than one night at home alone, this free time may not
mean anything to you. Meet a coupla new people so you can spruce up
your new-found freedom.
</P>
<P>
   CAPRICORN (Dec. 22 - Jan. 19): Everything from the grade on the
pop quiz to the party that awaits you at the end of the week is
rolling the right way. You cannot lose! You will have all of your
friends on your side if anyone tries to confront you this week.
Your friends are going to reveal to you a new side this week. They
will constantly be looking out for you.
</P>
<P>
   AQUARIUS (Jan. 20 - Feb. 18): Be supportive of all your friends
at all times, even when you do not completely agree with what they
have to say. Just like you need them, they, too, need to be
comforted in rough situations. When you do not know what to do, ask
your parents; they have been through everything and then some. They
are the best when it comes to advice. Learn that now.
</P>
<P>
   PISCES (Feb. 19 - March 20): Pretty soon you will be able to
spend days upon end with your friends, so take advantage of the
light homework you have and spend the time at home with the family.
Some families hardly ever see each other during the summer. But
your family will not suffer this year. Your older siblings make
great tutors and awesome company.
</P>
<P>
   ARIES (March 21 - April 19): You will soon have to bid farewell
to someone very dear to your heart. You two still have plenty of
time to make some wonderful memories before the departure. Use your
time wisely and be sure to have plenty of fun.
</P>
<P>
   TAURUS (April 20 - May 20): Something unbelievably crazy will
happen to you in the next few days. You may have to pinch your arm
to realize you aren't dreaming. Things like this do not happen
often, so take plenty of pictures and have a great time.
</P>
