<P>
   &UR; NATIONAL (a) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   SALMON-VIRUS (Undated) _ The mysterious virus that killed
Atlantic salmon at a Massachusetts fish hatchery last winter has
shown up in fish from three more Maine rivers, prompting a
multi-state scientific campaign to understand the disease before it
can threaten the dwindling population of the Northeast's premier
sportfish. By Scott Allen. 600 words.
</P>
