   RUSSIA-STEPASHIN (Moscow) _ The new prime minister, Sergei
Stepashin, won an easy confirmation vote Wednesday in the lower
house of parliament, bringing the brief political crisis to an
eerily peaceful end. By Celestine Bohlen.
</P>
<P>
   TELECOM-ITALIA (Rome) _ Telecom Italia's ambitious plan to merge
