<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-19 20:48 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3769 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FBN-CARDINALS-HNS &LR;      05-19 1083
