   Despite the frantic shuttle diplomacy of recent weeks, Rubin
said a diplomatic breakthrough was not yet at hand, as Washington
and Moscow remain far apart over the key issue of how to put
together a credible international security force to police any
peace arrangement in Kosovo.
</P>
<P>
   ``We are moving towards agreement, not away from agreement,''
