   &UR; WHO SAID WHAT &LR;
</P>
<P>
   ``I didn't write it. Someone else did. It's none of my
business.''
</P>
<P>
   _ &LR;   &LR; Kurt Vonnegut, in response to a New York Post reporter who
asked his opinion of ``Breakfast of Champions,''' the movie based
on his novel.
</P>
