   Over the top ( &UR; Gar Smith &LR; ); incredible ( &UR; Margaret MacDermott &LR; );
ambiguous ( &UR; Kate Williams &LR; ); postmodern ( &UR; Kay Franklin) &LR; ; pushing
the envelope ( &UR; Don Boyd &LR; ); hands-on ( &UR; Don Kingtoncq &LR; ); and much
much more ( &UR; Hobie McQuarrie &LR; ); and closure ( &UR; Bruce Steircq &LR; ).
</P>
