<HEADLINE>
FURRIN FROGS WILL SAVE FESTIVAL
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimlc!News Service clients) 
By ELIZABETH CAMPBELL 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   LAKE WORTH, Texas _$J,-Y  &QC; K-R.HI9Q% 12I9i%
</P>
</TEXT>
