<HEADLINE>
HOOKING KIDS INTO FISHING
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
(Adds informational chart) 
By BRETT PAULY  
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
